Let A= \left(
\begin{array}{ccc}
 1 & 0 & 0 \\
 0 & 0 & 1  \\
 0 & 1 & 0 \\
\end{array}
\right) \textrm{ and B=}  
\left(
\begin{array}{ccc}
 0 & 0 & 1  \\
 1 & 0 & 0  \\
 0 & 1 & 0 \\
\end{array}
\right)Compute the matrix products AB and BA

